violationsByInspectionidList.violationDescription: If provided, a water tank vent shall terminate in a downward direction and shall be covered with: 16 mesh screen or equivalent when the vent is in a protected area or A protective filter when the vent is in an area that is not protected from windblown dirt and debris.
violationsByInspectionidList.problemDescription: Does not terminate in downward direction

violationsByInspectionidList.violationDescription: EQUIPMENT shall be maintained in a state of repair and condition that meets the requirements of the code.
